<p>From what i understand and my experience. Dps is prolly the factor in your agro issues. But not in the way you think. Agro is generated by potential dps and not dps itself. You will get the same agro from max hits to no hits at all as long as the weapons have the same delay and damage bonus.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /> <br />What i suspect is the damage bonus is playing a big roll in agro at 28 delay from a 2hd weapon. I'm also pretty convinced that you're potentially doing more dps with the 2hs than with the one handers. You will have to parse it but im pretty sure your 2h easily beats your dw combo. I sure you were passing him up on the list. <br /> <br />When in pit groups and paly is tank in Anquish, Agro has become a lil frustrating. His dps is barely 150 and as a ranger I'm hitting 500dps with potential to do more with nukes. Paladins are not the agro magnets they were in the old days.</p>
